01:22:48.168 --> 01:22:49.127
Yeah. Yeah.

01:22:58.136 --> 01:22:59.096
Yeah.

01:23:01.139 --> 01:23:02.099
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:23:05.143 --> 01:23:07.104
