01:23:37.134 --> 01:23:40.095
I want you outside the door.
See that I am not disturbed.

01:23:41.138 --> 01:23:42.097
Right.

01:23:52.149 --> 01:23:54.109
- What about me?
- You go home.

01:23:56.153 --> 01:23:57.112
You sit by the phone.

01:23:59.156 --> 01:24:00.115
Can you do that?

01:24:03.160 --> 01:24:06.121
- What are you gonna do?
- I got some thinkin' to do.

01:24:06.163 --> 01:24:08.123
I gotta figure this thing out.

01:24:10.167 --> 01:24:12.127
I gotta have some privacy
to sit and think

01:24:12.169 --> 01:24:15.130
and figure how I'm gonna
handle this thing.

01:24:50.165 --> 01:24:52.125
- Yeah?
- Hey, Terry. It's me, Jackie.

01:24:54.169 --> 01:24:56.129
- Yeah, Jackie.
- Got a little job.

01:24:57.130 --> 01:25:00.092
Meet me at 43rd and Broadway.
About 11 o'clock, all right?

01:25:03.136 --> 01:25:05.097
- Can you get there?
- I'll be there.

01:25:05.138 --> 01:25:06.098
All right. See ya.

01:25:31.164 --> 01:25:32.124
(phone rings)

01:25:35.168 --> 01:25:38.130
Hi. Please
leave a message after the beep.

01:25:38.130 --> 01:25:40.090
 Hey, it's me. You there?

01:25:41.133 --> 01:25:42.092
Hello? Hello?

01:25:48.140 --> 01:25:50.100
Will you pick up if you're there?

01:25:53.145 --> 01:25:56.106
Look, we're in the middle of this thing.
You gotta understand.

01:25:56.148 --> 01:25:59.109
And I'm sorry. If I hurt you,
I'm sorry, all right?

01:26:01.153 --> 01:26:03.113
I'll get back. Good night.

01:26:25.135 --> 01:26:26.094
Hey, Terry.

01:26:34.144 --> 01:26:36.104
Where are we going? Beirut?

01:26:36.146 --> 01:26:39.107
Borelli's phoned Frankie.
We gotta come to this meeting.

01:26:41.151 --> 01:26:44.112
Cavello got wasted in the Kitchen
in the wee hours of the morning.

01:26:45.155 --> 01:26:46.114
- Cavello?
- Yeah.

01:26:47.157 --> 01:26:48.116
Is nobody safe?

01:27:01.129 --> 01:27:04.091
- You got the address?
- Yeah, right here.

01:27:04.132 --> 01:27:06.093
Get on down there now, OK? Get situated.

01:27:06.134 --> 01:27:09.096
It's just up from the restaurant.
Everything arranged.

01:27:09.137 --> 01:27:12.099
I arrive at noon. I don't call you
by two o'clock or Pat don't call you,

01:27:14.142 --> 01:27:17.104
you come in, tear 'em apart,
the spaghetti still on their spoons.

01:27:20.148 --> 01:27:22.109
You OK, Noonan?
Everything OK with you?

01:27:23.151 --> 01:27:26.113
- It'll be all right, Frankie.
- Yeah, either we're dead or we ain't.

01:27:34.162 --> 01:27:36.123
Anybody know how to get to Mott Street?

01:27:38.166 --> 01:27:39.126
Damn.

01:28:24.129 --> 01:28:25.088
Terry.

01:29:07.130 --> 01:29:10.092
...fold like a futon,
and the fuckin' frame's bent, right?

01:29:11.134 --> 01:29:14.096
So I bring it home. It looks easy.
I can't put the fuckin' thing together.

01:29:15.138 --> 01:29:18.100
So we called in a neighbour,
a guy with a very nice fuckin'...

01:29:20.143 --> 01:29:22.104
Let's get down to business.

01:29:22.145 --> 01:29:25.107
First of all, this problem we got here.
This is your responsibility.

01:29:28.151 --> 01:29:31.113
Either you get the respect
of your own people, or you got nothin'.

01:29:32.155 --> 01:29:35.117
My people, I let them go
at this thing on their own,

01:29:37.160 --> 01:29:40.122
your brother, he'd be in so many
fuckin' pieces right now,

01:29:40.163 --> 01:29:43.125
you couldn't put him back together
again even if you had directions.

01:29:45.168 --> 01:29:46.128
