I'm gonna have it solved for you.

01:30:23.165 --> 01:30:25.125
You understand that? Huh?

01:30:31.131 --> 01:30:34.092
You don't have to
worry about Frankie, man.

01:30:34.134 --> 01:30:37.095
And if he ain't OK, there'll be
a dumpster full of dead guineas,

01:30:38.138 --> 01:30:40.098
spaghetti still on their forks.

01:30:56.156 --> 01:30:57.115
Look...

01:30:59.159 --> 01:31:01.119
I could straighten the kid out.

01:31:02.162 --> 01:31:05.123
Jimmy Cavello was a great guy.
We all know this.

01:31:07.167 --> 01:31:08.126
But the kid...

01:31:12.130 --> 01:31:13.090
The kid...

01:31:15.133 --> 01:31:18.095
You should've been there
when I reamed him out over this.

01:31:18.136 --> 01:31:21.098
He'd have crawled in a hole
and brought the hole in with him,

01:31:21.139 --> 01:31:23.100
if he could find a hole to go into.

01:31:23.141 --> 01:31:26.103
Don't embarrass yourself, Frankie.
I know you don't want to insult me.

01:31:29.147 --> 01:31:30.107
No.

01:31:30.148 --> 01:31:33.110
But to be frivolous on a matter
of such importance is an insult.

01:31:35.153 --> 01:31:37.114
This fuckin' bum is your brother.

01:31:37.155 --> 01:31:40.117
So I understand your need to pursue
some hopeless course to try to save him.

01:31:42.160 --> 01:31:45.122
But everybody knows
what's gotta happen here.

01:31:46.164 --> 01:31:49.126
With every heartbeat, his miserable
fuckin' douche-bag life insults me.

01:31:55.132 --> 01:31:57.092
He's a thorn in my side, Frankie.

01:31:59.136 --> 01:32:02.097
Since we're together,
he's a thorn in your side.

01:32:04.141 --> 01:32:05.100
Now look, Frankie.

01:32:07.144 --> 01:32:09.104
I gotta know, and I gotta know now.

01:32:13.150 --> 01:32:16.111
Are you gonna be able to
pull this thorn out of our side?

01:32:26.163 --> 01:32:27.122
All right.

01:32:28.165 --> 01:32:30.125
This is your brother, Frank.

01:32:32.169 --> 01:32:35.130
So, for the sake of family and blood,
I'm gonna give you this opportunity.

01:33:18.131 --> 01:33:21.093
Looks like it's time
to kick some guinea ass.

01:33:22.135 --> 01:33:24.096
But he didn't call yet, Jackie.

01:33:25.138 --> 01:33:28.100
He said we don't go
untiI he called or Pat called.

01:33:29.142 --> 01:33:32.104
- That ain't what he said.
- Course it was. I was right there.

01:33:33.146 --> 01:33:35.107
- Richie, what'd he say?
- Who?

01:33:36.149 --> 01:33:38.110
- Frankie!
- About what?

01:33:38.151 --> 01:33:41.113
What are you askin' him for?
He's fuckin' stupid.

01:33:47.160 --> 01:33:49.121
Now, let's have some dessert.

01:33:53.166 --> 01:33:56.128
- I gotta make a call.
- Let the business wait.

01:33:57.170 --> 01:33:59.131
- Enjoy your dessert.
- It's my wife.

01:33:59.131 --> 01:34:01.091
Don't offend me, Frankie.

01:34:01.133 --> 01:34:04.094
You're gonna get up from my table
to call your wife?

01:34:06.138 --> 01:34:07.097
Let her wait.

01:34:12.144 --> 01:34:14.104
Don't fuck him up again.

01:34:14.146 --> 01:34:16.106
- That ain't what he said.
- It is what he said.

01:34:16.148 --> 01:34:19.109
- He said if he didn't call.
- No, if he did call.

01:34:20.152 --> 01:34:22.112
If we said... He said if we didn't call.

01:34:23.155 --> 01:34:25.115
- If he did.
- If he didn't.

01:34:25.157 --> 01:34:26.116
Did. Jack...

01:34:26.158 --> 01:34:29.119
I was in the truck.
He said if he didn't call.

01:34:29.161 --> 01:34:31.121
- No.
- If we didn't fuckin' call.

01:34:31.163 --> 01:34:34.124
- Where was I?!
- You were there too! You're fuckin' deaf!

01:34:35.167 --> 01:34:38.128
- He said if he didn't call.
- He said if he did call.

01:34:38.170 --> 01:34:39.129
- Relax.
- Richie.

01:34:41.131 --> 01:34:43.091
- I didn't hear him.
- He's fuckin' retarded!

01:34:43.133 --> 01:34:45.093
Nothing personal, Richard. You're stupid.

01:34:46.136 --> 01:34:48.096
That's not what he said.

01:34:50.140 --> 01:34:52.100
Jack, he said if he did call.

01:34:53.143 --> 01:34:55.103
If he called, we go. Otherwise no.

01:34:59.149 --> 01:35:01.109
Have a piece of cheesecake.

01:35:11.161 --> 01:35:13.121
Fuck me, man. This don't feel right.

01:35:14.164 --> 01:35:15.123
Fuck! Fuck! Fuck!

01:35:24.132 --> 01:35:25.092
Jack, calm down.

01:35:30.138 --> 01:35:33.100
-  Whoo!
- Jackie, Jackie, Jackie. Listen.

01:35:33.141 --> 01:35:36.103
He said if he did call...
Relax. Will you relax?

01:35:36.144 --> 01:35:39.106
- Terry, I love you, but you're wrong.
- I love you too, and I'm right.

01:35:40.148 --> 01:35:42.109
- He could be dying. Let's go.
- Jack...

01:35:43.151 --> 01:35:44.111
Let's go, huh?!

01:35:46.154 --> 01:35:49.116
You want me to make that call
for you, Mr Flannery?

01:35:49.157 --> 01:35:52.119
Tell your boy to stop
movin' around so much.

01:35:53.161 --> 01:35:55.122
He's interfering with my digestion.

01:36:01.169 --> 01:36:03.130
Have a cannoli. Some anisette.

01:36:08.135 --> 01:36:09.094
Just fucking go!

01:36:18.145 --> 01:36:19.104
 Let's go. Come on.

01:36:22.149 --> 01:36:24.109
I'm coming. I'm ready. All right.

01:36:30.157 --> 01:36:32.117
- You want your clock?
- No.

01:36:33.160 --> 01:36:35.120
Big mistake. Big mistake.

01:36:44.129 --> 01:36:47.090
Mr Borelli, I really do
gotta make a phone call.

01:36:47.132 --> 01:36:50.093
I must make it.
My wife's not been feeling well.

01:36:55.140 --> 01:36:56.099
With your permission.

01:36:59.144 --> 01:37:00.103
Go. Make your call.

01:37:01.146 --> 01:37:02.105
Thank you.

01:37:52.155 --> 01:37:54.116
See? She ain't even home.

01:38:08.130 --> 01:38:11.091
Either they forgot about us or
this entire neighbourhood better duck.

01:38:31.153 --> 01:38:34.114
All right. I want you to
drop me off at 39th Street.

01:38:36.158 --> 01:38:38.118
He ain't there! Frankie ain't there!

01:38:48.170 --> 01:38:50.130
Frank! It ain't a hit! It ain't a hit!

01:38:53.133 --> 01:38:55.093
- Let's get out of here!
- Move it!

01:38:57.137 --> 01:39:00.098
- It's all right.
- He was talking to him.

01:39:00.140 --> 01:39:01.099
I know. Turn around.

01:39:02.142 --> 01:39:03.101
What's this?

01:39:04.144 --> 01:39:07.105
Frankie, I hope you're not
lookin' to start a war here.

01:39:08.148 --> 01:39:10.108
In a war, we would crush you.

01:39:10.150 --> 01:39:11.109
You understand?

01:39:16.156 --> 01:39:19.117
Hey. Dumb fucks.
Don't know how close they came.

01:39:20.160 --> 01:39:21.119
It's your brother.

01:39:22.162 --> 01:39:24.122
My heart goes out to you.

01:39:40.138 --> 01:39:43.100
 What happened, apparently,
is that Borelli's got this beef with Cavello.

01:39:45.143 --> 01:39:48.105
Cavello failed to get permission
from Borelli to take out Stevie,

01:39:49.147 --> 01:39:51.108
which pissed Borelli off
cos of this thing with us.

01:39:51.149 --> 01:39:54.111
And there was probably some
other secretive guinea bullshit too.

01:39:56.154 --> 01:39:58.115
