01:39:59.157 --> 01:40:00.117
No.

01:40:02.160 --> 01:40:05.122
And as a kind of bonus
he's sendin' over 25 grand.

01:40:05.163 --> 01:40:08.125
All we gotta do is drop a couple of
Haitians who are on his drug turf.

01:40:10.168 --> 01:40:12.129
He's sendin' over
the first instalment tonight.

01:40:12.170 --> 01:40:14.131
- You wanna pick it up?
- Sure.

01:40:16.133 --> 01:40:17.092
Good.

01:40:20.137 --> 01:40:22.097
It's unbelievable, huh?

01:40:23.140 --> 01:40:25.100
The way things turn out.

01:40:28.145 --> 01:40:29.104
Yeah.

01:40:33.150 --> 01:40:36.111
I gotta catch a shower, and some fresh
clothes. I've been in this shit for days.

01:40:39.156 --> 01:40:42.117
The pick-up's at 11.
I'll let you know where.

01:40:43.160 --> 01:40:46.121
I want to keep this hush-hush, OK?
Just you and me. It's a lot of money.

01:40:47.164 --> 01:40:50.125
St Patty's is coming up, so we'll have
a little loose change to celebrate with.

01:40:54.129 --> 01:40:55.088
Hey, Jack.

01:40:59.134 --> 01:41:00.093
Come here.

01:41:14.149 --> 01:41:16.109
- You ain't done that for years.
- Yeah.

01:41:42.135 --> 01:41:43.095
- Hey.
- Hey.

01:41:47.140 --> 01:41:50.102
I missed you at the club. What's goin' on?

01:41:51.144 --> 01:41:53.105
Gotta work untiI 11 or so.

01:41:55.148 --> 01:41:57.109
We can hoot and holler after that.

01:41:57.150 --> 01:42:00.112
Like, I can meet you at the club about 12.

01:42:03.156 --> 01:42:05.117
- Want a beer?
- Sure.

01:42:10.163 --> 01:42:12.124
- You OK?
- I'm feeling fucked up.

01:42:15.168 --> 01:42:17.129
I gotta make a pick-up.

01:42:17.170 --> 01:42:20.132
25 grand. Borelli's got some
bullshit Haitian problems.

01:42:26.138 --> 01:42:28.098
Pick-up's at Battery Park.

01:42:34.146 --> 01:42:36.106
I'm fuckin' beat, man.

01:42:37.149 --> 01:42:40.110
I'm gonna ask Frankie
for a little time off.

01:42:40.152 --> 01:42:42.112
I've been working hard.

01:42:45.157 --> 01:42:47.117
So, the parade's coming up.

01:42:49.161 --> 01:42:51.121
Wouldn't that be nice?

01:42:51.163 --> 01:42:54.124
You, me and Kate can go celebrate
St Patty's Day together.

01:42:58.170 --> 01:43:00.130
Go see the parade. Wanna?

01:43:01.131 --> 01:43:03.091
Listen, Jackie. I heard something.

01:43:09.139 --> 01:43:12.100
- I hear Frankie put the hit on Stevie.
- What?

01:43:14.144 --> 01:43:16.104
Hey, hey, hey! Get out!

01:43:16.146 --> 01:43:19.107
That is my fuckin' brother
you're talking about, huh?!

01:43:20.150 --> 01:43:22.110
- I heard it.
- Yeah, you heard it!

01:43:22.152 --> 01:43:25.113
