01:48:07.145 --> 01:48:08.105
Hey, Frankie.

01:48:11.149 --> 01:48:12.109
Hi, Jackie.

01:48:14.152 --> 01:48:17.114
- I thought you were the guineas.
- The guineas ain't coming.

01:48:18.156 --> 01:48:21.118
- It's just you and me.
- It's just you and me?

01:48:22.160 --> 01:48:23.120
Yeah.

01:48:38.135 --> 01:48:40.095
Just tell him to get down here!

01:48:46.143 --> 01:48:47.102
Jack!

01:49:45.160 --> 01:49:48.121
What the hell is going on?
You tell us one place

01:49:48.163 --> 01:49:51.124
but the shooters are all
at some other goddamn place!

