my eyes cut out of my head.

01:50:01.134 --> 01:50:03.095
And I'd fuckin' deserve it.

01:50:04.137 --> 01:50:06.098
I ain't your goddamn social worker.

01:50:06.139 --> 01:50:09.101
Now you just tell me
who whacked out Jack Flannery.

01:50:11.144 --> 01:50:14.106
- I don't know.
- What do you mean, you don't know?

01:50:14.147 --> 01:50:16.108
- You were here.
- I wasn't fuckin' here.

01:50:16.149 --> 01:50:19.111
I was over at that phone booth calling you.

01:50:19.152 --> 01:50:22.114
I should have backed up Jack,
but I was over there doin' my rat job.

01:50:23.156 --> 01:50:26.118
Was Flannery here, or his boy?
Who did you see?

01:50:26.159 --> 01:50:29.121
I don't want to do this
any more, all right?!

01:50:29.162 --> 01:50:32.124
I ain't cut out for this undercover shit!
Get yourself an Italian, cos I quit.

01:50:34.167 --> 01:50:37.129
We're on these suckers!
It's just a matter of timing!

01:50:37.170 --> 01:50:38.130
- Timing?
- Yeah!

01:50:38.130 --> 01:50:41.091
These guys don't know what century it is.
And you talk about fucking timing?

01:50:44.136 --> 01:50:45.095
You know what I did?

01:50:47.139 --> 01:50:50.100
I got my best friend killed.
I got Jack killed. That's what I did.

01:50:51.143 --> 01:50:53.103
But it's fucking over.

01:50:53.145 --> 01:50:55.105
Look at me. See? I quit. Good night.

01:50:58.150 --> 01:50:59.109
- Terry.
- Fuck you.

01:51:07.159 --> 01:51:08.118
Hey, Noonan!

01:51:16.168 --> 01:51:17.127
Fucked up, man.

01:51:33.143 --> 01:51:34.102
Kathleen.

01:51:36.146 --> 01:51:37.105
Hi.

01:51:43.153 --> 01:51:46.114
Nobody even knows
what he was doing out there.

01:52:15.143 --> 01:52:16.103
I'm sorry.

01:52:23.151 --> 01:52:25.112
I couldn't have saved Jackie, could I?

01:52:31.159 --> 01:52:34.121
Even though I know it's not true,
I feel I could have.

01:52:40.168 --> 01:52:42.129
But I should have told him what you were.

01:53:17.164 --> 01:53:18.123
Here, Jack.

01:53:21.168 --> 01:53:23.128
You're bound to get thirsty.

01:53:41.146 --> 01:53:42.105
Hey, Terry.

01:53:48.153 --> 01:53:49.112
How's Kathleen?

01:53:51.156 --> 01:53:54.117
She's holding up pretty good.
She's strong. But it's hard.

01:53:57.162 --> 01:53:59.122
It's you I'm worried about.

01:54:00.165 --> 01:54:01.124
What do you mean?

01:54:05.170 --> 01:54:08.131
Do you know where I was
the night this happened?

01:54:11.134 --> 01:54:12.094
I was on Pier 84.

01:54:27.150 --> 01:54:30.112
Noonan, if you and me
are on a collision course,

01:54:32.155 --> 01:54:34.116
that would not be very smart of you.

01:54:38.161 --> 01:54:40.122
You know how smart you are?

01:54:46.169 --> 01:54:48.130
That's how smart you are.

01:55:05.147 --> 01:55:06.106
He's dead.

01:55:07.149 --> 01:55:09.109
The fuck's dead. Do you see that?

01:55:10.152 --> 01:55:11.111
Motherfucker.

01:55:26.168 --> 01:55:27.127
Who is it?

01:55:29.129 --> 01:55:30.088
 Kate?

01:55:34.134 --> 01:55:37.095
Kate, I feel awful
about the things I was.

01:55:40.140 --> 01:55:43.101
Kate, you just gotta give me
a minute on this, all right?

01:55:48.148 --> 01:55:51.109
If you don't want me here, just tell me.
But let me see your face so I believe it.

01:55:53.153 --> 01:55:56.114
Terry, I'm telling you the truth.
I'm telling you the God's truth.

01:55:59.159 --> 01:56:02.120
Bastard! You're dragging me in,
making me part of it!

01:56:02.162 --> 01:56:04.122
You want me to drown?
I gotta save my life!

01:56:04.164 --> 01:56:07.125
I know, but I need to explain.
I need you to understand.

01:56:07.167 --> 01:56:09.127
- I understand.
- You're not listening.

01:56:10.170 --> 01:56:12.130
Would you just fuckin' listen?

01:56:23.141 --> 01:56:25.102
I thought some things.
I could come back.

01:56:30.148 --> 01:56:32.109
I always hated that I'd run away.

01:56:33.151 --> 01:56:36.113
Had nothing to do with you, except I knew
if I tried to tell you, I'd never get away.

01:56:45.163 --> 01:56:48.125
So I was in Boston. I just ended up there.

01:56:55.132 --> 01:56:57.092
It seemed far enough away.

01:57:02.139 --> 01:57:05.100
It come to me then. It just happened.
These things happen.

01:57:06.143 --> 01:57:08.103
Other things happen. It's your life.

01:57:15.152 --> 01:57:18.113
They were looking for somebody to go
undercover who knew the Kitchen,

01:57:19.156 --> 01:57:20.115
who was known.

01:57:23.160 --> 01:57:26.121
I could've said no,
but I thought I could do it.

01:57:28.165 --> 01:57:31.126
It was like this opportunity.
I could look the entire thing in the eye.

01:57:32.169 --> 01:57:35.130
You'd be married, forgotten about me.
And Jack, I would leave him out of it.

01:57:40.135 --> 01:57:42.095
But it was only an idea.

01:57:45.140 --> 01:57:48.101
Nothing to do with the truth. It was just...

01:57:50.145 --> 01:57:52.105
a fuckin' idea, like...

01:57:56.151 --> 01:57:58.111
you believe... in angels or the saints

01:58:01.156 --> 01:58:04.117
or that there's such a thing
as a state of grace,

01:58:06.161 --> 01:58:07.120
and you believe it.

01:58:11.166 --> 01:58:13.126
But it's got nothing to do with reality.

01:58:15.170 --> 01:58:18.131
It's just an idea. You got
your ideas and you got reality.

01:58:23.136 --> 01:58:24.096
They're all...

01:58:31.144 --> 01:58:33.105
They're all fucked up.

01:58:53.166 --> 01:58:54.126
I was going out.

01:58:56.169 --> 01:58:58.130
I gotta go. I gotta get ready.

01:59:02.134 --> 01:59:05.095
He's someone I met at work.
He's taking me out for a drink.

01:59:10.142 --> 01:59:12.102
- Frank killed Jack.
- Did he?

01:59:20.152 --> 01:59:22.112
I gotta go down now. He's waiting.

01:59:27.159 --> 01:59:29.119
- You're cold, Kate.
- Yes, I am.

01:59:31.163 --> 01:59:34.124
I don't mind you got a date.
I really don't.

01:59:34.166 --> 01:59:36.126
I ain't jealous. I got a date, too.

01:59:41.131 --> 01:59:44.092
Is there something you want me
to tell Frankie for you when I see him?

01:59:47.137 --> 01:59:49.097
Make sure, when you leave,
the button's pushed in

01:59:49.139 --> 01:59:52.100
and the door's pulled tight before you go.

02:00:09.159 --> 02:00:11.119
- What did you find out, Pat?
- Nobody knows him.

02:00:11.161 --> 02:00:14.122
- They must've brought him from Boston.
- From Boston, to rat us out.

02:00:15.165 --> 02:00:18.126
Don't matter where
the cocksucker's from. He's dead.

02:00:19.169 --> 02:00:22.130
It's 15,000 when he takes his last breath.
You bring me his rat head, it's 30,000.

02:00:34.142 --> 02:00:36.103
- Where the fuck is he?
- Check it out.

02:00:41.149 --> 02:00:43.110
What the fuck are you doin'?

